@startuml
actor Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "customer-service" as CustomerService
participant "product-service" as ProductService
database "Product DB" as ProductDB
database "MySQL Customer DB" as CustomerDB

Customer -> Gateway: PUT /api/customers/cart/items/{id}/
Gateway -> CustomerService: PUT /customers/cart/items/{id}/
CustomerService -> CustomerService: Validate JWT customer
CustomerService -> ProductService: GET current product detail
ProductService -> ProductDB: Check stock
ProductDB --> ProductService: Product stock
ProductService --> CustomerService: Product detail
CustomerService -> CustomerDB: Update quantity/subtotal
CustomerDB --> CustomerService: Updated cart item
CustomerService --> Gateway: Update success
Gateway --> Customer: Cart item updated
@enduml
